title: Drugs Inc. - Season 5 Complete [HDTV]
description:
This is a collection of downloaded episodes for National Geographic Drugs Inc Season 5.  I have not seen a complete Season 5 torrent hit as of yet so I figured I would try to give back to the community :-).  These were collected during the airing of Season 5 and are either base HDTV quality or 1 or 2 are 720p.  They were the best copies I could find at the time, and I am sorry I can not remember all the credits for these episodes.  If you can somehow identify an episode as one you uploaded at some point please leave a comment so you can get your due congratulations and I for one am super grateful folks take the time to keep uploading sweet sweet content :-D.
